dc_title_s: Voting Wards City of Milwaukee, WI 2016
dc_description_s: This data represents voting wards for the City of Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 2016. [Contains voting ward boundaries and associated polling place information. Ward boundaries were updated in 2016. Any updates to this dataset since 2016 will represent changes to polling place information in the ward attribute table. For more information: http://city.milwaukee.gov/election]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data, please visit: https://data.milwaukee.gov/dataset/voting-wards
